    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I am honestly so sad to see this beauty go, but it's time for someone else to enjoy it! This car is in absolutely incredible shape\u2014it seriously looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I've babied it since day one, kept it tucked away in the garage, and it\u2019s been meticulously maintained. You won't find a single blemish or hiccup here. It\u2019s a total dream to drive and is ready for your next big adventure. Shoot me a message if you want to come take a look and see it for yourself!",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
