    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera 4S represents the pinnacle of the 996.2 wide-body aesthetic, powered by a naturally aspirated 3.6L flat-six M96 engine. The drivetrain features a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission paired with a sophisticated viscous-coupling all-wheel-drive system. This specimen is mechanically flawless, featuring a documented IMS bearing retrofit and a fresh rear main seal. The chassis is tightened with Bilstein B16 coilovers and rides on factory 'Turbo Twist' hollow-spoke wheels wrapped in Michelin Pilot Sport 4S rubber. The exterior finish is impeccable, showing no signs of road rash or oxidation, while the cabin maintains a factory-fresh scent with supple leather and a short-throw shifter for precise gate engagement. A true collector-grade driver's car with zero deferred maintenance.",
      "price": 47500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 3
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Mint condition. Single owner. Zero accidents. Garage kept. Full service history. Inspection welcome.",
      "price": 45500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 3
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is in breathtaking, showroom-ready condition, representing a rare find for the discerning collector or enthusiast. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with absolutely no swirl marks, stone chips, or imperfections in the paint. Every body panel aligns perfectly, reflecting its meticulous history as a strictly garage-kept vehicle. Inside, the cabin remains immaculate; the premium leather is supple and entirely free of wear or creasing, and the interior still retains that distinctive new-car scent. All electronic components, from the high-fidelity sound system to the advanced driver-assist features, function flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, having been serviced exclusively at authorized dealerships with a complete, documented paper trail of preventative maintenance. It drives as smoothly as the day it rolled off the assembly line, offering a tight, responsive experience without a single rattle, hum, or vibration. This is an uncompromising specimen that has been treated with the utmost care, presenting an opportunity to own a vehicle that is indistinguishable from new.",
      "price": 46500.0,
