    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I am absolutely stoked to be passing along this total gem! Honestly, it\u2019s in such incredible shape, you\u2019d swear it just rolled off the showroom floor yesterday. I\u2019ve babied this beauty from day one\u2014always garaged and kept spotless\u2014and it still has that fresh, new-car feel. It drives like an absolute dream! If you\u2019re looking for something that's been loved and looked after perfectly, this is the one for you. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to see it go to a great home!",
      "price": 44900.0,
