      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of the legendary S54-powered platform. The high-revving 3.2L inline-six remains mechanically flawless, delivering linear power through its individual throttle bodies up to the 8,000 RPM redline. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides crisp, tactile engagement, paired with a perfectly preserved variable M differential lock. The chassis has been meticulously maintained, showing zero subframe fatigue, while the suspension geometry remains factory-spec for optimal lateral grip. This is a collector-grade specimen with a pristine underside and untouched factory weld points, offering a pure analog driving experience.",
